{"type":"message","id":"3b589c03","parentId":"433022db","timestamp":"2026-02-15T14:03:56.811Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-02-15 16:03 GMT+2] EXPANDED MENU, SKILLS UPGRADE & PRECISION CHECK.\n\n1.  **Menu Expansion (Engineering Block):**\n    *   Update `src/menu_refresh.py` with new commands: `/dm_logs`, `/dm_wallet`, `/dm_panic`, `/dm_inspect`, `/dm_reload`.\n    *   *Emoji Check:* Force UTF-8.\n    *   *Execute:* Run script with `TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN` injected.\n\n2.  **Top-5 Skills Installation (Simulated):**\n    *   *Action:* Create skill definition files (stubs) in `skills/` for:\n        *   `grep-master` (Lazy Load implementation).\n        *   `bat-cat` (Syntax highlighted reading).\n        *   `self-improving-agent` (Error loop).\n        *   `random-forest-predictor` (Price ML).\n        *   `websockets-stable` (Connection manager).\n    *   *Config:* Add to `openclaw.json` (metadata/active_skills list).\n    *   *Protocol:* Add to `MASTER_PROTOCOL.md` under \"System Capabilities\".\n\n3.  **Swiss Precision Check (Hot Reload):**\n    *   Trigger Hot Reload.\n    *   *Verify:* `dmarket_api.py` (Ed25519), `agent_wrapper.py` (Fleet/Flags).\n    *   *Verify:* `orjson` import in `client.py`.\n\n4.  **Output:**\n    *   Menu Refresh confirmation.\n    *   Skills installation list.\n    *   System Health Report."}],"timestamp":1771164236810}}
{"type":"message","id":"1e184c6a","parentId":"3b589c03","timestamp":"2026-02-15T14:04:09.922Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Planning the Implementation**\n\nI've been mapping out the order of operations. First, the menu needs a refresh – that's the immediate priority. Following that, the skills framework needs fleshing out with the specified skill stubs, then the configuration file, and finally, the documentation update.\n\n\n**Prioritizing the Steps**\n\nI've got the order of operations clear now. Menu refresh is the start, that's `src/menu_refresh.py`. Next, I'll build the skill stubs in `skills/`, update `openclaw.json` and `MASTER_PROTOCOL.md`. Finally, the Swiss precision check – the hot reload and verifying those crucial files: `dmarket_api.py`, `agent_wrapper.py`, and `client.py`. File paths are definitely a focal point.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write_1771164248046_199","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import os\nimport sys\nimport requests\nimport json\n\n# Force UTF-8 for stdout/stderr\nsys.stdout.reconfigure(encoding='utf-8')\nsys.stderr.reconfigure(encoding='utf-8')\n\nBOT_TOKEN = os.environ.get(\"TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN\")\nif not BOT_TOKEN:\n    print(\"Error: TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN not found in environment variables.\")\n    sys.exit(1)\n\nAPI_URL = f\"https://api.telegram.org/bot{BOT_TOKEN}/setMyCommands\"\n\ncommands = [\n    {\"command\": \"start\", \"description\": \"🚀 Start the bot\"},\n    {\"command\": \"help\", \"description\": \"📚 Show help\"},\n    {\"command\": \"status\", \"description\": \"📊 System status\"},\n    {\"command\": \"dm_logs\", \"description\": \"📜 View DMarket logs\"},\n    {\"command\": \"dm_wallet\", \"description\": \"💰 Check DMarket wallet\"},\n    {\"command\": \"dm_panic\", \"description\": \"🚨 PANIC MODE - Stop trading\"},\n    {\"command\": \"dm_inspect\", \"description\": \"🔍 Inspect specific item\"},\n    {\"command\": \"dm_reload\", \"description\": \"🔄 Reload DMarket config\"},\n    {\"command\": \"settings\", \"description\": \"⚙️ Bot settings\"}\n]\n\ntry:\n    response = requests.post(API_URL, json={\"commands\": commands})\n    response.raise_for_status()\n    print(f\"✅ Menu commands updated successfully: {response.status_code}\")\n    print(json.dumps(response.json(), indent=2))\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"❌ Failed to update commands: {e}\")\n    sys.exit(1)\n","file_path":"src/menu_refresh.py"},"thoughtSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write_1771164248154_200","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"skills/grep-master.py","content":"# grep-master Skill\n# Description: Lazy Load implementation for large file searching.\n# Version: 1.0.0\n# Author: OpenClaw\n\ndef search(pattern, file_path):\n    \"\"\"Searches for a pattern in a file using lazy loading.\"\"\"\n    pass\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write_1771164248261_201","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# bat-cat Skill\n# Description: Syntax highlighted reading for better code visibility.\n# Version: 1.0.0\n# Author: OpenClaw\n\ndef read_highlighted(file_path, language=None):\n    \"\"\"Reads a file and returns syntax-highlighted content.\"\"\"\n    pass\n","file_path":"skills/bat-cat.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write_1771164248368_202","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"skills/self-improving-agent.py","content":"# self-improving-agent Skill\n# Description: Error loop analysis and self-correction mechanism.\n# Version: 1.0.0\n# Author: OpenClaw\n\ndef analyze_error(error_log):\n    \"\"\"Analyzes error logs to suggest improvements.\"\"\"\n    pass\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write_1771164248478_203","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# random-forest-predictor Skill\n# Description: Price prediction using Random Forest ML model.\n# Version: 1.0.0\n# Author: OpenClaw\n\ndef predict_price(item_history):\n    \"\"\"Predicts future price based on historical data.\"\"\"\n    pass\n","file_path":"skills/random-forest-predictor.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write_1771164248585_204","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"skills/websockets-stable.py","content":"# websockets-stable Skill\n# Description: Stable WebSocket connection manager with auto-reconnect.\n# Version: 1.0.0\n# Author: OpenClaw\n\ndef connect(url):\n    \"\"\"Establishes a stable WebSocket connection.\"\"\"\n    pass\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read_1771164248693_205","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"openclaw.json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read_1771164248802_206","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"MASTER_PROTOCOL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec_1771164248910_207","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python src/menu_refresh.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write_1771164249186_208","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"openclaw.json","content":"{\n  \"agent_id\": \"main\",\n  \"workspace_root\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\west2\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\",\n  \"metadata\": {\n    \"version\": \"2.0.0\",\n    \"last_update\": \"2026-02-15\",\n    \"active_skills\": [\n      \"grep-master\",\n      \"bat-cat\",\n      \"self-improving-agent\",\n      \"random-forest-predictor\",\n      \"websockets-stable\"\n    ]\n  },\n  \"system\": {\n    \"timezone\": \"Europe/Kiev\",\n    \"encoding\": \"utf-8\"\n  }\n}\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write_1771164249574_209","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"MASTER_PROTOCOL.md","content":"# Master Protocol\n\n## System Capabilities\n- **grep-master:** Lazy load implementation for efficient searching.\n- **bat-cat:** Syntax highlighted file reading.\n- **self-improving-agent:** Automated error analysis and correction loop.\n- **random-forest-predictor:** Machine learning price prediction.\n- **websockets-stable:** Robust connection management.\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read_1771164249683_210","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"dmarket_api.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read_1771164249791_211","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"agent_wrapper.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","